snippet.description:
The FBI Just DESTROYED Amber Heard's Case And Career | The Gossipy

Welcome toThe Gossipy. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

Ever since the divorce of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp was filed, there has been a stream of new information leaked in regard to their strange situation. 

Amber Heard accused Johnny Depp of several horrifying things throughout the course of their marriage. However, more evidence has been discovered that proves a lot of what she has claimed has been false. 

After a recent victory in the United Kingdom, it is clear that Amber Heard will stop at nothing to get the case to go her way, while Depp is doing the same.
